  "attachmentHtml": "\n<p><strong>PC Number: </strong>2019-0243<br></p><p><strong>Date: </strong>2019-03-25</p><hr><p>\n\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nWhereas the judges whose names are set out in the attached schedule have requested, with the approval of their respective Chief Justice, that they be granted leave of absence from their judicial duties from September 1, 2019 until April 30, 2020, in order to participate in the National Judicial Study Leave Fellowship Program;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nTherefore, Her Excellency the Governor General in Council, on the recommendation of the Minister of Justice, pursuant to paragraph 54(1)(b) of the <em>Judges Act</em>, approves of leave of absence being granted to those judges whose names are set out in the attached schedule from September 1, 2019 until April 30, 2020.</p>\n<br style=\"page-break-before:always\">\n<p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nAttendu que les juges dont le nom figure à&nbsp;l’annexe ci-jointe ont demandé la permission, avec l’autorisation de leur juge en chef respectif, de prendre congé du 1<sup>er</sup> septembre 2019 au 30 avril 2020 pour participer au Programme national de bourses universitaires à l’intention des&nbsp;juges,\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nÀ ces causes, sur recommandation du ministre de la Justice et en vertu de l’alinéa 54(1)b) de la <em>Loi sur les juges</em>, Son Excellence la Gouverneure générale en conseil autorise l’octroi d’un congé aux juges dont le nom figure à l’annexe ci-jointe pour la période allant du 1<sup>er</sup> septembre 2019 au&nbsp;30&nbsp;avril 2020.\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;</p>\n<br style=\"page-break-before:always\">\n<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nSCHEDULE\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nThe Honourable Donna L. Shelley \n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nCourt of Queen’s Bench of Alberta\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nThe Honourable Guylène Beaugé\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nSuperior Court of Quebec\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nThe Honourable Frank J. Pizzitelli\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nTax Court of Canada\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nThe Honourable Darla A. Wilson\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nSuperior Court of Justice of Ontario\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nThe Honourable Martin Vauclair\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nCourt of Appeal of Quebec\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nThe Honourable Jeanne E. Watchuk\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nSupreme Court of British Columbia</p>\n<br style=\"page-break-before:always\">\n<p style=\"text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.11in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nANNEXE\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nL’honorable Donna L. Shelley\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nCour du Banc de la Reine de l’Alberta\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nL’honorable Guylène Beaugé\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nCour supérieure du Québec\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nL’honorable Frank J. Pizzitelli\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nCour canadienne de l’impôt\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nL’honorable Darla A. Wilson\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nCour supérieure de justice de l’Ontario\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nL’honorable Martin Vauclair\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nCour d’appel du Québec\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nL’honorable Jeanne E. Watchuk\n</p><p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\nCour suprême de la Colombie-Britannique\n</p><p style=\"text-indent:1.00in;text-align:left;margin-top:0.00in;margin-bottom:0.00in;\">\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p></p><form method=\"post\" action=\"index.php\"><input type=\"submit\" value=\"Back to Form\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" name=\"return\"></form>\t\t\n        <!-- end main content -->\n        <div id=\"def-preFooter\">\n       \t\t<!-- Write closure fall-back static file -->\n             <!--Response.Write readFile(\"StaticFallbackFiles/gcweb/preFooter-\" & $lang & \".html\") -->\n        </div>\n\t\t<!-- Write closure template -->\n        <script type=\"text/javascript\">\n            var defPreFooter = document.getElementById(\"def-preFooter\");\n            defPreFooter.outerHTML = wet.builder.preFooter({\n                cdnEnv: \"prod\",\n                dateModified: \"2022-07-11\",\n                showPostContent: true\n            });\n        </script>\n    "
